- cs.SD (Software Engineering) could be a possible category as the paper may involve developing algorithms for data collection, face image analysis, and trend mining.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) could be a possible category as the paper deals with sensitive topics such as drug use and privacy concerns related to social media data mining.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) could be a possible category as the paper deals with public health and law enforcement issues related to drug use.
